   <abstract>Draft of statement Senator Kefauver will not continue as chairman or member of the Senate Crime Investigating Committee, and gives a fairly extensive descriptions of why he has made the decision. The reasons include the mission of the investigation being completed and his devotion to other causes, including his Atlantic Union resolution which he hopes will bring peace to the world, most pressingly in Korea.</abstract>
